Catherine Spencer is a popular Canadian writer of over 40 romance novels in Harlequin Enterprises Ltd since 1986 . She also signed her books as Kathy Orr . Catherine Spencer went to a Catholic school . She worked as High School English teacher . She married and had four children and some dogs . When the menopause approached , Catherine began to write . She publised her firt novel in 1986 . With friend and fellow writer Judith Bowen , she is a co - sponsor of the biennial Singletree Workshop , an weekend retreat for romance writers . Now , Spencer lives with her husband in White Rock , in south of Vancouver , British Columbia . Their four children are adults , and they have five grandchildren . That Man Callahan ! . 